101 of the very best goals.

Over 300 goals were scored in the Premier League this season, and we have selected 101 of the best! Included are goals from the top strikers in Premier League football.

Ian Wright Since his ?2.5 Million move from Palace to Arsenal, his tremendous goal scoring power has earned him recognition from the fans and the England manager Graham Taylor.

Eric Cantona His shock ?1 million pound move from Leeds to Manchester delighted the United faithful and his contribution to their title victory was priceless.

Dean Saunders An unsuccesssful spell at Liverpool found Deano at Aston Villa where as a player he has had his most promising season yet, almost winning a championship medal.

Teddy Sheringham Replacing Gary Lineker at White Hart Lane was the job Steady Teddy had to do, his response a flurry of goals.
